{{obsolete}}
{{flavour|Surrounds the caster with a mobile ring of highly-damaging thunderclouds.}}

'''Ring of Thunder''' is a monster-only spell that surrounds the user with a ring of [[Cloud#Thunder|thunder clouds]], which periodically deal heavy [[electricity]] damage to creatures standing in them. Much like [[Ring of Flames]], new clouds are constantly created around the user as they move.

The following enemies cast Ring of Thunder:
* {{monsterlink|Bai Suzhen (dragon)}}

==History==
*This spell was removed in [[0.26]]. Instead, [[Bai_Suzhen#Dragon_Form|Bai Suzhen]] and some [[pandemonium lord]]s got a permanent '''Ring of X''' enchantment that surrounds them with an appropriate cloud ring.

[[Category:Monster spells]]
